Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:21.56,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish you were here，and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:28.04,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:33.84,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I have been looking for my own style
